snippet.title: Super Mario Land - Birabuto Kingdom Acapella
snippet.description:
An original a-cappella arrangement of Birabuto Kingdom from Super Mario Land for the Game Boy!

This song will forever remind me of sitting inside on a warm summer day playing Super Mario Land.  For such a short game with not-so-great controls, I enjoyed the heckkkk out of this little Mario title.  The music is fantastic, and the fact that I could play Mario sitting on my porch made me fall in love.  The later Super Mario Land games refined everything quite a bit, but this game still has a special place in my heart.
